</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[163,1070,520,571]" pageId="7" pageNumber="1264">
E t y m o l o g y: The species is named in honour to the late Heinrich Wolf, a leading expert of 
<taxonomicName box="[260,378,549,571]" class="Insecta" family="Pompilidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="1264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Pompilidae</taxonomicName>
, who collected the 
<typeStatus box="[573,665,549,571]" pageId="7" pageNumber="1264">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
